    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! It is honestly in incredible shape\u2014I've babied this car since day one, and it still looks and smells like it just left the showroom. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for something that's basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! I'd love for you to come take a look and see for yourself how special it is!",
      "price": 43200.0,
