    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car is in flawless condition, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish free of any stone chips, swirls, or scratches. The interior is equally impeccable; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or creasing, and every trim piece remains tight and rattle-free. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule with all service records documented in a comprehensive binder. It has been stored in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover and has never seen rain or snow. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this vehicle offers a 'new car' experience for the next owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
